<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Change Your Password</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Account Created by Admin - Password Change Required</h1>

  <p>Dear <%= @user.username %>,</p>
  <p>
    An admin has created an account for you. For security reasons, we require you to change your password immediately.
